@node "ack" "Acknoledgement"

 Very big thanks to Manuel Lemos: almost all the features of EpsLab came from
his suggestions after I released BinEps.

 In particular, Manuel suggested the use of the 'post.library' to render the
preview image; he suggested where to find the TIFF documents, and suggested to
add the EPSI format support.
 He also did a great beta-testing job, and helped making the GUI closer to
Commodore's (or should now I say Amiga International's ?) style-guide.

                Thanks Manuel!

-----

