@node "history" "Revision history"

 ------------
 Version 1.02
 ------------

    First release.

    Being EpsLab the successor of BinEps, here you can find what's new
    from BinEps.

    - Full font-sensitive gui.

    - Full localization.

    - Ability to create a crossbox preview.

    - Ability to render a full preview using 'post.library'.

    - Ability to create a compressed or uncompressed TIFF preview.

    - Ability to create an ASCII preview (EPSI file format).

    - Automatic conversion of some single-page PostScript to EPSF, with bounding
        box recalculation.
    
    - Selectable density for the preview image.

    - Selectable page size for PostScript to EPSF conversion.
@endnode
